tent_length": 46, "attachs": [{"attachurl": "mon_202606/03/jmQ6-i8z5ZbT3cSpe-gy.jpg", "size": 112, "type": "img", "subid": 0, "url_utf8_org_name": "image%2epng", "dscp": "", "path": "mon_202606/03", "name": "jmQ6-i8z5ZbT3cSpe-gy.jpg", "ext": "jpg", "thumb": "120"}], "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780445571}, {"pid": 870422314, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 60, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-03 08:22", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=870421939,45974302,6352]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=64626308]hua8493[/uid] (2026-06-03 08:18):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，我昨天又品了几遍这段话，但是又有了一些新的疑问，所以这波924至今的底层逻辑做的是放水牛，AI牛只是走到现在消息和资金催化的结果？结果就是去年还是全面牛市，现在就是结构性牛市一样？[/quote]<br/>放水第一阶段是大水漫灌，然后是精准滴灌 你不管是我们的政策 还是国外的政策都是一样的。或者说所有政策的流程都是如此<br/>放到市场里面  第一阶段就是一浪铺开找主线，然后三浪已经确定了主线，就只涨主线<br/>具体的看我的之前写的了 不重复 这些我之前长篇都是写得很清楚的。", "lou": 2902, "content_length": 249, "reply_to": 870421939, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780446166}, {"pid": 870424053, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 109, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-03 08:40", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "你们看有色的不要用周期的眼光去看  如果这样看至少在炒股的逻辑内都是错的<br/>现在的有色甚至不跟期货<br/>而是只要跟AI硬件需求有关的才行，就像为什么昨天铜大涨你们知道么，因为老黄在演讲的时候提了 能用铜尽量用铜链接，实在不行再用光，因为相对铜的目前价格低一些。<br/>所以你们搞清楚 你们是来干嘛的 是来投资 还是陪公司成长，还是单纯的想挣钱。", "lou": 2903, "content_length": 312, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780447253}, {"pid": 870431843, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 129, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-03 09:39", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "哈哈哈哈！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！", "lou": 2904, "content_length": 62, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780450758}, {"pid": 870435480, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 289, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-03 10:02", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "知道什么是炒股么？半导体强的时候吃了半导体   光强的时候吃了光 <br/>我有没有叫你们切换  你们懂什么叫投资 什么叫炒股么？<br/>连链条都给你们梳理了<br/>不仅是半导体的链条还是光的链条<br/>你们再不能赚钱 那就退市吧", "lou": 2905, "content_length": 180, "14": {"13": 6, "12": 1}, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780452124}, {"pid": 870437822, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 72, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-03 10:17", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[img]./mon_202606/03/jmQ6-el6oK6T1kSa4-1j.jpg[/img]<br/>双跌停再生我止盈了。收益4个点。", "lou": 2906, "content_length": 67, "attachs": [{"attachurl": "mon_202606/03/jmQ6-el6oK6T1kSa4-1j.jpg", "size": 7, "type": "img", "subid": 0, "url_utf8_org_name": "image%2epng", "dscp": "", "path": "mon_202606/03", "name": "jmQ6-el6oK6T1kSa4-1j.jpg", "ext": "jpg", "thumb": "56"}], "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780453022}, {"pid": 870438856, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 170, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-03 10:23", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=870438236,45974302,6368]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67091234]牛牛去哪儿了[/uid] (2026-06-03 10:19):[/b]<br/><br/>光什么时候百万撤离，涨害怕了[s:ac:喘][/quote]<br/>我刚和龟哥说 如果他敢现在卖 我马上冲到那边砍死他 然后让她老婆改嫁   这是原话。", "lou": 2907, "content_length": 77, "reply_to": 870438236, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780453419}, {"pid": 870440718, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 59, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-03 10:34", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[b]Reply to [pid=870439521,45974302,6370]Reply[/pid] Post by [uid=42633665]Hugvn_1[/uid] (2026-06-03 10:27)[/b]<br/>信我这个本地人的就行了", "lou": 2908, "content_length": 52, "reply_to": 870439521, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780454062}, {"pid": 870442142, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 34, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-03 10:43", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "conten