70445719, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780455945}, {"pid": 870447401, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 37, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-03 11:14", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=870446647,45974302,6380]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67145444]sentser[/uid] (2026-06-03 11:10):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，我是废物[s:ac:瞎][s:ac:瞎][s:ac:瞎][s:ac:瞎][img]./mon_202606/03/jmQ6-3vkzZbT1kShs-13q.jpg[/img][/quote]<br/><br/>[img]./mon_202606/03/jmQ6-dew5K8T1kSap-1i.jpg[/img]<br/>所以这就是你们的问题了 我严格按我的战法操作。", "lou": 2913, "content_length": 85, "attachs": [{"attachurl": "mon_202606/03/jmQ6-dew5K8T1kSap-1i.jpg", "size": 8, "type": "img", "subid": 0, "url_utf8_org_name": "image%2epng", "dscp": "", "path": "mon_202606/03", "name": "jmQ6-dew5K8T1kSap-1i.jpg", "ext": "jpg", "thumb": "56"}], "reply_to": 870446647, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780456498}, {"pid": 870449686, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 143, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-03 11:29", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "你们真是本末倒置<br/>光前三 就3只票<br/>二线光 10只<br/>光纤  5只<br/>光上游10只<br/>边缘光 超过50只<br/>你们确定性的时候不炒  MD去找那种不确定的？你们不是韭菜谁是韭菜啊", "lou": 2914, "content_length": 132, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780457374}, {"pid": 870455639, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 84, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-03 12:08", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=870454303,45974302,6390]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67201175]憬然又春天[/uid] (2026-06-03 11:58):[/b]<br/><br/>哎呀，不太对，今天怎么科技涨5个点，我的不涨就算了 还能跌？不太对 破位了我先出来看看<br/>[s:ac:哭笑]现在是到这一步了嘛[/quote]<br/>下一波才是<br/>你们应该多看看我写的小剧场<br/>真的 没一句是废话的。", "lou": 2915, "content_length": 61, "reply_to": 870454303, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780459700}, {"pid": 870455974, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 55, "score_2": 0, "re